                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Aquilonius <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Fab</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> Statutus <lb n="3"/>P&amp;lt;a=E&amp;gt;<expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex>avio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XV <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Apol</abbr><ex>linaris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XVIIII <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXXVI <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Antonius <lb n="7"/><surplus>ius</surplus> Longus <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>eres</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciundum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zeile 1: NI-Ligatur; Zeile 4: IP-Ligatur; Zeile 6/7 Doppelung -ius/ius. Über dem gerahmten Inschriftfeld mit Girlanden verbundene Säulen, über den Girlanden Kopf (Gorgoneion?). Bei Mosser; Genser unrichtige Literaturangabe (AE 1929, 199).</p>
